description.narrative: The budget advocacy and support to budget preparation resulted in higher level of readiness of selected Line Ministries to engage in budget negotiations using the programme-based budgeting framework, including for social protection, child protection and education. At sub-national level, through successful and facilitation of the dialogue between the Ministry of Interior and the Ministry of Economy and Finance (MEF), the agreement has been forged to ensure earmarking of up to 25 % of the Commune/Sangkat budgets for social services. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
